        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Admittedly, the past few years for Harley-Davidson have involved a fair number of ups and downs. However, few would have predicted that in May of 2022 the company would be shutting down production. Before you start panicking, this shutdown is only temporary, but it doesn’t bode well not only for the future of Harley but the motorcycle industry in general.",
